title: Friday Night Bingo (New Jersey Ska Punk)
description:
Friday Night Bingo was a ska punk band formed by some dudes in New Jersey in 2009. I'm not sure. This is all of their songs available on the internet (and some not, I assume) in one compiled tracklist. 


All files have been normalized for likeness in volume, as these were mostly pulled from different sources. These songs are partially from a disc sent to a friend of mine directly from a guy in the band (I think?). 


To my knowledge, they had only one official release, the EP "Scientists Of The World". This entire disc is included in this compilation. 


This band is no more, but I hope someday some guy in this band finds this compilation in a torrent or something and is surprised at the small but faithful following they have/had.
